  <entry>
    <title>功能句写作</title>
    <link href="http://example.com/2021/03/03/%E5%9B%9B%E5%85%AD%E7%BA%A7%E5%86%99%E4%BD%9C/"/>
    <id>http://example.com/2021/03/03/%E5%9B%9B%E5%85%AD%E7%BA%A7%E5%86%99%E4%BD%9C/</id>
    <published>2021-03-03T14:20:53.467Z</published>
    <updated>2021-03-03T15:38:02.292Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><h2 id="一-功能句写作（命题作文）"><a href="#一-功能句写作（命题作文）" class="headerlink" title="一.功能句写作（命题作文）"></a>一.功能句写作（命题作文）</h2><h3 id="一-话题引起"><a href="#一-话题引起" class="headerlink" title="(一)话题引起"></a>(一)话题引起</h3><p>1.人们慢慢认识到….</p><p>There is a growing worldwide/national awareness of + （主题词）n/doing</p><p>tip：an increasing global ,  international , concern over (往往倾向于负面话题或批判类话题)</p><ul><li>2008.一次性塑料袋使用的问题</li><li>There is a growing worldwide awareness of the problem of disposable(不可分解/降解) plastic bags among the public.</li><li>2013.06 人们慢慢意识到学习基本技能的重要性.</li><li>There is a growing worldwide awareness of the importance of learning basic skills,</li></ul><p>2.~~~引起了人们广泛的讨论</p><p>There has been a heated discussion about …sth/doing sth</p><p>tip: wide/deep/profound   talk/debate/concern</p><ul><li><p>2011.06 在线购物 online shopping</p></li><li><p>There has been a heated discussion about (the impact of ) online shopping.</p></li><li><p>2012.06 Excessive packaging 过度包装</p></li><li><p>There has been a heated discussion about (the harm of ) excessive packaging.</p></li><li><p>2013.12 网络对学习的影响</p></li><li><p>There has been a heated discussion about the impact of the Internet on learning.</p><p>tip: the impact of A on B</p></li></ul><p>3.当前，有这样一种增长的趋势是：…</p><ul><li>There is a growing tendency nowadays that + 句子…</li></ul><p>tip: trend   at present=now</p><ul><li><p>2011.6 网购</p><ul><li>There is a growing tendency nowadays that <u>more and more people are buying goods online.</u></li></ul><p>tip：an increasing number of –</p><ul><li>people in mounting numbers are purchasing products on the internet.</li></ul></li></ul><p>4.近来，…的问题引发了…关注.</p><ul><li><p>201.06 过度包装</p></li><li><p>Recently,the problem of “excessive packaging （主题词）” has aroused wide/deep/great/profound（深刻的） concern among the public.</p><p>tip: arouse（引发）~~provoke（激发/唤起）</p><ul><li><p>Recently—In recent years / decade,</p></li><li><p>Problem—Issue/ situation / phenomenon</p></li></ul></li><li><p>2013.12 低头族</p><ul><li><p>Recently , the problem of “phubbing “ has aroused wide/deep/great concern among the public.</p><p>tip: phubbing == phone + snub(冷漠)     rely on mobilephone</p></li></ul></li></ul><p>5.无人不知，无人不晓</p><ul><li>Nobody could have failed to notice the fact that … has become a grave（-负） problem / popular （+正）phenomenon in China.<ul><li>2017.12 医患关系</li><li>Nobody could failed to notice the fact that the relationship between doctors and patients has become a grave problem in China.</li></ul></li></ul>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
