  <entry>
    <title>CSS—盒子模型</title>
    <link href="http://example.com/2021/02/04/css%E4%B9%8B%E7%9B%92%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B/"/>
    <id>http://example.com/2021/02/04/css%E4%B9%8B%E7%9B%92%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B/</id>
    <published>2021-02-04T12:17:08.424Z</published>
    <updated>2021-02-08T15:37:55.115Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><p>[TOC]</p><h2 id="1-网络布局"><a href="#1-网络布局" class="headerlink" title="1.网络布局"></a>1.网络布局</h2><p>本质：</p><ol><li>首先利用css设置好盒子的大小，然后摆放盒子的位置。</li><li>最后把网页元素，eg：文字图片等，放入盒子内。                        </li></ol><p>.2.盒子模型</p><p>Box Model : 把HTML页面中的布局元素看作是一个矩形的盒子，也就是一个承装内容的容器</p><h2 id="2-summary："><a href="#2-summary：" class="headerlink" title="2.summary："></a>2.summary：</h2><ol><li>boxmodel包含元素内容，边框（border），内边距（padding），外边距（margin）</li><li>model内的文字和图片等元素是内容区域</li><li>盒子的厚度就是盒子的border</li><li>盒子内容与边框的距离是内边距（类似单元格cellpadding）</li><li>盒子与盒子之间的距离是外边距（类似单元格cellspacing）</li></ol><h2 id="3-border"><a href="#3-border" class="headerlink" title="3.border"></a>3.border</h2><ul><li><p>语法：</p><figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">border : border-width || border-style || border-color </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><table><thead><tr><th>属性</th><th></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>border-width</td><td>形容粗细，px</td></tr><tr><td>border-style</td><td>框样式：none ;solid;dashed(虚)；dotted（点线）</td></tr><tr><td>border-color</td><td>框颜色</td></tr></tbody></table><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;!DOCTYPE <span class="meta-keyword">html</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">html</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">head</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">meta</span> <span class="attr">charset</span>=<span class="string">&quot;utf-8&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">title</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">title</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">style</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">&quot;text/css&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">div &#123;</span><br><span class="line">width: 100px;</span><br><span class="line">height: 100px;</span><br><span class="line">border-width: 3px;</span><br><span class="line">border-style: dotted;</span><br><span class="line">border-color: red;  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="css">              <span class="comment">/* 汇总写法： border：3px dotted red; 无顺序*/</span></span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">style</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">head</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">body</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">body</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">html</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="4-盒子边框的细化"><a href="#4-盒子边框的细化" class="headerlink" title="4.盒子边框的细化"></a>4.盒子边框的细化</h2><p>上边框：border-top-style   border-top-width    border-top-color  border-top:宽 样式 颜色</p><p>下边框:   border-bottom- style ````</p><p> 左边框：border-left-style</p><p> 右边框：border-right-style</p><p>简便写法：   </p></li></ul><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">border:none;</span><br><span class="line">border-top:5px solid yellow;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="5-表格的细线框"><a href="#5-表格的细线框" class="headerlink" title="5.表格的细线框"></a>5.表格的细线框</h2><p>边框重叠如何解决：</p><ul><li><p>cellspacing=‘0’时，单元格之间会重叠；</p></li><li><p>边框加粗，可通过css属性</p><figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="selector-tag">table</span>&#123; <span class="attribute">border-clooapse</span>:collapse;&#125; <span class="comment">/*collapse 意思为合并*/</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>eg：</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">head</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">meta</span> <span class="attr">charset</span>=<span class="string">&quot;utf-8&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">title</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">title</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">       <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">style</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">table&#123;</span><br><span class="line">width: 200px;</span><br><span class="line">height: 200px;</span><br><span class="line">border: 5px solid red;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">td&#123;</span><br><span class="line">border: 5px solid blue;</span><br><span class="line">text-align: center;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">table,td&#123;</span><br><span class="line">border-collapse: collapse;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">style</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">head</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="6-内边距padding"><a href="#6-内边距padding" class="headerlink" title="6.内边距padding"></a>6.内边距padding</h2></li><li><p>padding- left  </p></li><li><p>padding-right</p></li><li><p>padding-top</p></li><li><p>padding-bottom </p></li></ul><h5 id="指定了padding后："><a href="#指定了padding后：" class="headerlink" title="指定了padding后："></a>指定了padding后：</h5><ol><li><p>内容和边框有了距离，添加了内边距</p></li><li><p>盒子变大</p><h5 id="简写：padding：1-2-3-4个值"><a href="#简写：padding：1-2-3-4个值" class="headerlink" title="简写：padding：1/2/3/4个值"></a>简写：padding：1/2/3/4个值</h5><table><thead><tr><th align="left">个数</th><th>意思</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="left">1</td><td>上下左右</td></tr><tr><td align="left">2</td><td>上下     左右</td></tr><tr><td align="left">3</td><td>上    左右    下</td></tr><tr><td align="left">4</td><td>顺时针：上 右 下 左</td></tr></tbody></table><ol><li><p>要求盒子有一个左边内边距是 5像素</p></li><li><p>要求简写的形式写出  一个盒子上下是 25像素   左右是15像素。</p></li><li><p>要求简写的形式写出 一个盒子  上内边距是 12像素  下内边距是 0  左内边距是 25像素  右内边距是 10像素</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">style</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="css">          <span class="comment">/* 1 */</span></span></span><br><span class="line">div&#123;</span><br><span class="line">padding-left: 5px;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="css">          <span class="comment">/* 2 */</span></span></span><br><span class="line">div&#123;</span><br><span class="line">padding: 25px 15px;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="css">          <span class="comment">/* 3 */</span></span></span><br><span class="line">div&#123;</span><br><span class="line">padding: 12px 10px 0 25px;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">style</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol></li></ol><h2 id="7-外边距margin"><a href="#7-外边距margin" class="headerlink" title="7.外边距margin"></a>7.外边距margin</h2><p>作用：控制盒子和盒子之间的距离</p><ul><li>margin-left </li><li>margin-right</li><li>margin-top</li><li>margin-bottom</li></ul><p>简写方法同padding一样：1/2/3/4.</p><h2 id="8-块级盒子水平居中"><a href="#8-块级盒子水平居中" class="headerlink" title="8.块级盒子水平居中"></a>8.块级盒子水平居中</h2><ul><li>实现条件：<ul><li>盒子必须指定宽度</li><li>左右外边距设置为auto</li></ul></li></ul><p>常见三种写法：</p><ul><li><p>.class {width：200px; margin:0 auto;}</p></li><li><p>.class {width: 200px; margin: auto;}</p></li><li><p>.class {width: 200px; margin-left:auto; margin-right:auto;}</p></li></ul><h3 id="tip（注意区分）"><a href="#tip（注意区分）" class="headerlink" title="tip（注意区分）:"></a>tip（注意区分）:</h3><ul><li><p>文字居中与和盒子居中的区别：</p><p>盒子内文字/行内/行内块元素  居中：text-align : center;</p><p>盒子居中：eg：margin: 10px auto;</p></li></ul><figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="selector-tag">text-align</span>: <span class="selector-tag">center</span>; <span class="comment">/*  文字 行内元素 行内块元素水平居中 */</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="selector-tag">margin</span>: 10<span class="selector-tag">px</span> <span class="selector-tag">auto</span>;  <span class="comment">/* 块级盒子水平居中  左右margin 改为 auto 就阔以了 上下margin都可以 */</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>插入图片和背景图片的区别：</li></ul><ol><li><p>插入图片： eg：产品展示类 移动位置只能靠盒模型 padding margin</p><p>2.背景图片一般用于小图标背景 or 超大背景图片   通过 background-position改位置。</p></li></ol><figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="selector-tag">img</span> &#123;  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="attribute">width</span>: <span class="number">200px</span>;<span class="comment">/* 插入图片更改大小 width 和 height */</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attribute">height</span>: <span class="number">210px</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="attribute">margin-top</span>: <span class="number">30px</span>;  <span class="comment">/* 插入图片更改位置 可以用margin 或padding  盒模型 */</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attribute">margin-left</span>: <span class="number">50px</span>; <span class="comment">/* 插入图片也是一个盒子 */</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="selector-tag">div</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="attribute">width</span>: <span class="number">400px</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="attribute">height</span>: <span class="number">400px</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="attribute">border</span>: <span class="number">1px</span> solid purple;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="attribute">background</span>: <span class="number">#fff</span> <span class="built_in">url</span>(images/sun.jpg) no-repeat;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attribute">background-position</span>: <span class="number">30px</span> <span class="number">50px</span>; <span class="comment">/* 背景图片更改位置 我用 background-position */</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="9-清楚元素默认内外边距"><a href="#9-清楚元素默认内外边距" class="headerlink" title="9.清楚元素默认内外边距"></a>9.清楚元素默认内外边距</h2><ul><li><p>制作网页时：</p><figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">* &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attribute">padding</span>: <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attribute">margin</span>: <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><h6 id="行内元素照顾兼容性，尽量只设置左右内外边距，不设置上下内外边距。"><a href="#行内元素照顾兼容性，尽量只设置左右内外边距，不设置上下内外边距。" class="headerlink" title="行内元素照顾兼容性，尽量只设置左右内外边距，不设置上下内外边距。"></a>行内元素照顾兼容性，尽量只设置左右内外边距，不设置上下内外边距。</h6></li></ul><h2 id="10-内外边距合并"><a href="#10-内外边距合并" class="headerlink" title="10.内外边距合并"></a>10.内外边距合并</h2><ul><li><h4 id="相邻块元素垂直外边距的合并"><a href="#相邻块元素垂直外边距的合并" class="headerlink" title="相邻块元素垂直外边距的合并"></a>相邻块元素垂直外边距的合并</h4><ul><li>当上下相邻的两个块元素相遇时，如果上面的元素有下外边距margin-bottom</li><li>下面的元素有上外边距margin-top，则他们之间的垂直间距不是margin-bottom与margin-top之和</li><li><strong>取两个值中的较大者</strong>这种现象被称为相邻块元素垂直外边距的合并（也称外边距塌陷）。</li></ul></li><li><p>嵌套元素垂直外边距的合并（塌陷）</p><ul><li>对于两个嵌套关系的块元素，如果父元素没有上内边距<strong>paddin-top</strong>及边框<strong>border</strong></li><li>父元素的上外边距<strong>margin-to</strong>p会与子元素的上外边距<strong>margin-top</strong>发生合并</li><li>合并后的外边距为两者中的<strong>较大者</strong>！</li></ul></li></ul><p><strong>解决方案：</strong></p><ol><li>可以为父元素定义上边框<strong>border-top</strong></li><li>可以为父元素定义上内边距<strong>padding-top</strong></li><li>可以为父元素添加<strong>overflow:hidden</strong></li></ol><h2 id="11-盒子模型布局稳定性"><a href="#11-盒子模型布局稳定性" class="headerlink" title="11.盒子模型布局稳定性"></a>11.盒子模型布局稳定性</h2><p>按照 稳定性排序,  优先使用  宽度 （width）  </p><p>其次 使用内边距（padding）    </p><p>再次  外边距（margin）。   </p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">width &gt;  padding  &gt;   margin   </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li><p>原因：</p><ul><li><p>margin 会有外边距合并</p></li><li><p>padding 会影响盒子大小，需要进行加减计算</p></li><li><p>width 没有问题。</p></li></ul></li></ul><h2 id="12-圆角边框（CSS3）"><a href="#12-圆角边框（CSS3）" class="headerlink" title="12.圆角边框（CSS3）"></a>12.圆角边框（CSS3）</h2><ul><li><p>语法：</p><figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="selector-tag">border-radius</span>: <span class="selector-tag">length</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>其中每一个值可以为 数值 or 百分比 形式</p></li><li><p>技巧： 让一个正方形，变成⚪；</p><figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="selector-tag">border-radius</span>: 50%；</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>矩形的圆角， 就不要用 百分比了，因为百分比会是表示高度和宽度的一半。</li><li>而我们这里矩形就只用 用 高度的一半就好了。精确单位。eg:淘宝搜索框。</li></ul></li></ul><h2 id="13-盒子阴影（CSS3"><a href="#13-盒子阴影（CSS3" class="headerlink" title="13.盒子阴影（CSS3)"></a>13.盒子阴影（CSS3)</h2><ul><li><p>语法：</p><figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="selector-tag">box-shadow</span>: 水平阴影 垂直阴影 模糊距离（虚实） 阴影尺寸（影子大小） 阴影颜色 内/外阴影；</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>前两个属性必须写，其余可省略；</p></li><li><p>外阴影(outset)是默认的，但是不能写，想要内阴影可写（inset）</p><figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="selector-tag">div</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attribute">width</span>: <span class="number">200px</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attribute">height</span>: <span class="number">200px</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attribute">border</span>: <span class="number">10px</span> solid blue;</span><br><span class="line">   <span class="comment">/* box-shadow: 5px（水平位置） 5px（垂直位置） 3px（模糊距离） 4px（阴影尺寸/影子大小） rgba(0, 0, 0, .3)（阴影颜色）inset（内阴影）; */</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="attribute">box-shadow</span>: <span class="number">0</span> <span class="number">15px</span> <span class="number">30px</span> <span class="built_in">rgba</span>(<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">0</span>, .<span class="number">4</span>) inset;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
